=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719eb48fb5acf27858a4e52ef3b023394267e5a2","tid":1997403,"uid":141789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fedcd4e863d3f01f5f6b30a8b87e8924b030af9c","tid":1997403,"uid":2008,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但搵得omakase食就想搵間有曬omakase應有程序嘅店，btw thx巴打，有冇好推介"},{"pid":"7cc594f5a9638acbacc6655293c7ca83a1296c5c","tid":1997403,"uid":141789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d995725829b1a2e12851cba81910b93e1436267","tid":1997403,"uid":133354,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:34:58.000Z","msg":"食過一次lunch,  total 4人，坐房<br />\n<br />\n拎壽司上嚟，待應話次序由左下食到右上咁啦(類似),  隔離個fd遲少少到，待應拎壽司上嚟，發現個擺位同我嗰個唔同，但待應講個次序都係一樣由左下食到右上，大家先知待應9up<br />\n<br />\n食晒壽司，即上甜品同埋單，但只係食咗一個鐘，想趕我地走咁款，餐飯每人都食三四百，咁既態度真係好難接受<br />\n<br />\n壽司有一半係幾好食，有一半就壽司郎級數，整體嚟講係：無下次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成一半係壽司郎級數就不了，壽司郎只不過比爭鮮好嗰些少"},{"pid":"960be219b15f7b934fd3b1254342b9df6e6a8a60","tid":1997403,"uid":124970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"咁貴要儲錢 平平地食住龍門先"},{"pid":"5b0224aa27e6934c22b6d4da7775c055b56ee8c2","tid":1997403,"uid":301551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:14:41.000Z","msg":"搭單問<br />\n有無巴絲食過大埔鮨魂呢"},{"pid":"29bfb588a7e97d78c120d97b1a1014b5063881c7","tid":1997403,"uid":231179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b0224aa27e6934c22b6d4da7775c055b56ee8c2","tid":1997403,"uid":301551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,